item.description:

Identified by scraper @ 2024-09-13T09:14:00+00:00

  • Incident Date: 2024-08-16
  • City: ELKRIDGE
  • State: MD
  • Report Type: A hazardous material incident
  • Mode Of Transportation: Highway
  • Carrier/Reporter: A. DUIE PYLE INC.
  • Hazmat Fatalities: 0
  • Hazmat Injuries: 0
  • Non-Hazmat Fatalities: 0
  • Total Amount Of Damages: 0
  • Serious Incident Ind: No
  • Description: When unloading freight from trailer it was observed that a drum was slightly leaking from the bottom area of it. Further investigation revealed that it appeared the drum had been struck and slightly punctured by a forkblade from a forklift which consequently contributed to the unintentional release. Spilled material was neutralized and placed into a recovery container. The punctured drum was repaired with drum repair putty and placed into a recovery container as well.
